S.FORM: = Teldreka = Gaga mniq Kawsyungsu Mawrincyu ka alang Teldreka. 262 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 876 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 93% niqan 815 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 7% niqan 61 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Rukai 76%, Paiwan 7%, Bunun 6%, Amis 2%, Cou 1%.
